org.gradoop.common.model.api.entities

Interface Attributed

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Edge, Element, GraphElement, GraphHead, Vertex
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EPGMEdge, EPGMElement, EPGMGraphElement, EPGMGraphHead, EPGMVertex, TemporalEdge, TemporalElement, TemporalGraphElement, TemporalGraphHead, TemporalVertex

    public interface Attributed
    Used to describe entities that can have properties.

        Adds a given property to that entity. If a property with the same key does not exist, a new property will be created. Otherwise, the existing property value will be overwritten by the given value.
